title: Baker Mayfield, Jon Gruden, Cowboys, Aaron Rodgers
itunes:title: Baker Mayfield, Jon Gruden, Cowboys, Aaron Rodgers
description:
Colin disagrees with Baker Mayfield’s comments on changing, gives his prediction for the Cleveland Browns this season, what the Dallas Cowboys need to do, and why he feels Aaron Rodgers is playing the victim. Guests include Greg Jennings, Clarence Hill, Cris Collinsworth, and Lincoln Kennedy.
